Engine (generic skeletons only — the plugin stays domain-free):
- identity: one part may nest 2-3 sub items (the STRAC form / お金のブロック
  パズル — 売上＝変動費＋限界利益; 限界利益＝固定費＋利益). Sub column stacks
  to exactly the parent's height; identityTextSpec is the single source for
  thin-slice handling (honest proportions kept, TYPE steps down head->small —
  builder draws and gate measures with the same numbers). Lint: one-sub rule,
  sub 2-3, all-or-none values, 縦計算 cross-checks (IDENTITY-SUM WARN on
  parts-vs-whole and sub-vs-parent drift), emphasis+subEmphasis => ERROR.
- breakeven (CVP / 損益分岐点図): 売上高線 × 総費用線 (固定費 floor + 変動費
  slope) crossing at BEP, 損失/利益 regions. TERMS only, never value labels;
  honest crossing from {fixed, variableRate}; without data the engine
  auto-stamps ※模式図 (machine-checked). v>=1 => CAPACITY (no 限界利益).

Knowledge (project-side, NOT plugin — the design-doc/DESIGN.md split):
- docs/canon/accounting-fp-insurance.md: 会計/FP/保険の正準形カタログ
  (~30 concept->skeleton mappings with honesty guards) + GAP台帳
  (document-mock, coverage decay).
- skills/domain-canon: the factory skill — inventory concepts, gate each form
  (structure-word / symbol-erasure / honesty), map to skeletons, file GAPs as
  recipe proposals, emit docs/canon/<domain>.md. deck-strategy now loads
  docs/canon/*.md at the beat->pattern step.

Verified: STRAC textbook case renders both levels at exact proportions
(1.272/1.908, 1.341/0.447in; sub flush to parent, d<=0.001in); breakeven data
vs schematic stamp machine-checked; torture-09 extended (2-sub, dual emphasis,
sum drift, v=1.2); run-gate PASS across all 6 themes; validate PASS.
